'''薩德伯里中微子觀測站實驗室'''（{{lang|en|'''SNOLAB'''}}，簡稱為「薩實驗室」）是位於[[加拿大|加拿大]][[安大略省|安大略省]][[大薩德伯里|薩德伯里]]2100米深的[[镍|镍]]矿中的地下物理實驗室。原本位於此處的[[薩德伯里微中子觀測站|薩德伯里微中子觀測站]]（Sudbury Neutrino Observatory，縮寫為SNO）實驗計畫已結束，但其設施已被擴張成為永久物理實驗室。

薩實驗室乃是全世界在地下比較深處的幾個實驗設施之一。在地下2316米深處{{le|果拉爾金礦的粒子實驗|Particle experiments at Kolar Gold Fields}}因礦場關閉而於1992年終止運作。<ref>{{cite journal|title=Status of India-based Neutrino Observatory (INO)|author=Naba K. Mondal|url=http://www.imsc.res.in/~ino/OpenReports/Insa/naba.pdf|date=January 2004|journal=Proc Indian Natn Sci Acad|accessdate=2007-08-28|issue=1|volume=70|pages=71–77|archive-date=2013-07-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130709173407/http://www.imsc.res.in/~ino/OpenReports/Insa/naba.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|title=The Kolar Gold Fields Neutrino Experiment. II. Atmospheric Muons at a Depth of 7000 hg cm-2 (Kolar)|author=M. R. Krishnaswamy et al.|date=6 July 1971|journal=Proceedings of the Royal Society of London. Series A, Mathematical and Physical Sciences|issue=1555|volume=323|pages=511-522|jstor=78071}}</ref>正在計畫中的{{le|DUSEL|Sanford Underground Research Facility}}實驗室也已大幅度縮減，由於[[國家科學基金會|國家科學基金會]]拒絕負擔主要開支。<ref>{{Cite web|title=DUSEL no more|url=https://www.bhpioneer.com/local_news/dusel-no-more/article_5c46ec6e-af25-11e0-aeb5-001cc4c03286.html|access-date=2022-04-21|last=Pioneer|first=Wendy Pitlick Black Hills|work=Black Hills Pioneer|language=en|quote=Lesko said the scaled back plans boil down to just one underground research campus. Originally, lab officials planned to build a major surface campus, a science campus 4,850 feet underground that included two lab modules, and a smaller lab module campus 7,400 feet underground. The Sanford Underground Research Facility, Lesko said, focuses on building just one campus at the 4,850-foot level that will host experiments in dark matter, double beta decay, and long baseline neutrino research.}}</ref>2010年開始運作的[[中国锦屏地下实验室|中国锦屏地下实验室]]在那時是全世界最深的地下實驗室，緲子通量低於0.2 μ/m²/day ，<ref name="JinPing">{{Cite journal|title=Measurement of cosmic ray flux in the China JinPing underground laboratory|url=https://iopscience.iop.org/article/10.1088/1674-1137/37/8/086001|last=Wu|first=Yu-Cheng|last2=Hao|first2=Xi-Qing|date=2013-08|journal=Chinese Physics C|issue=8|doi=10.1088/1674-1137/37/8/086001|volume=37|pages=086001|issn=1674-1137|arxiv=1305.0899|bibcode=2013ChPhC..37h6001W|last3=Yue|first3=Qian|last4=Li|first4=Yuan-Jing|last5=Cheng|first5=Jian-Ping|last6=Kang|first6=Ke-Jun|last7=Chen|first7=Yun-Hua|last8=Li|first8=Jin|last9=Li|first9=Jian-Min}}</ref>薩實驗室的緲子通量為0.27 μ/m²/day。<ref name="handbook">{{Citation|title=SNOLAB User’s Handbook Rev. 2|page=13|url=http://snolab2008.snolab.ca/snolab_users_handbook_rev02.pdf|date=2006-06-26|accessdate=2013-02-01}}</ref> （與之相比，在海平面，緲子通量大約為15 million μ/m²/day。)

雖然與礦坑相連通，實驗室本身維持於[[潔淨室|級別2000]]標準的[[潔淨室|潔淨室]]狀況，即尺寸不小於1μm的粒子少於2000個每1 m3空氣，背景輻射也很低．在其上方有2070 m石頭，約6010 {{le|米水當量|meter water equivalent}}（MWE）的屏蔽，足可擋去大部分的[[宇宙射線|宇宙射線]]，是設置高{{le|靈敏度 (電子設備)|sensitivity (electronics)|靈敏度}}與超低計數率實驗夢寐以求的良好環境。<ref name="handbook" />

== 歷史 ==

薩實驗已獲得重大成功，並且展示出地下深處物理實驗室的寶貴價值，很多基礎物理問題都可以從在地下深處完成的物理實驗獲得答案，例如，在太陽內部進行核融合的狀況、中微子的質量、暗物質的探測等等重要問題。2002年，{{le|加拿大創新基金會|Canada Foundation  for Innovation}}批准，將薩觀測站擴張成為一所永久性世界級實驗研究中心，<ref>{{cite press release|title=Canada selects 9 projects to lead in international research|url=http://www.innovation.ca/en/AboutUs/News/Canadaselects9projectsleadininternationalresearch|publisher=Canada Foundation for Innovation|date=2002-06-20|accessdate=2007-09-21}}</ref>該實驗室分別又在2007年與2008年獲得更多資金。<ref>{{cite press release|title=Province Supports Expansion of World's Deepest Lab Administered by Carleton University|url=http://newsroom.carleton.ca/2007/08/21/province-supports-expansion-of-worlds-deepest-lab-administered-by-carleton-university/|publisher=Carleton University|date=2007-08-21|accessdate=2007-09-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120818084234/http://newsroom.carleton.ca/2007/08/21/province-supports-expansion-of-worlds-deepest-lab-administered-by-carleton-university/|archive-date=2012-08-18|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite press release|title=New Funding will Support Underground Lab Operations as SNOLAB nears Completion|url=https://www.snolab.ca/sites/default/files/SnolabNewsRelease-2008-01-22.pdf|publisher=SNOLAB|date=2008-01-18|accessdate=2008-02-26}}</ref>

== 實驗 ==
[[File:DEAP3600.jpg|thumb]]
在薩實驗室裏，主要有六個正在進行的物理實驗： <ref name="current_ex">{{Cite web|title=Experiments|url=https://www.snolab.ca/science/experiments/|access-date=2022-04-21|work=SNOLAB|language=en-US}}</ref><ref name="andes2014">{{Cite conference|url=http://andeslab.org/workshop4/talks/Noble-ANDES2014.pdf|title=Dark Matter Physics at SNOLAB and Future Prospects|first=Tony|last=Noble|date=2014-01-31|conference=Fourth International Workshop for the Design of the ANDES Underground Laboratory|conference-url=http://andeslab.org/workshop4/}}</ref>{{Rp|2}}
*{{le|氦與鉛觀測站|Helium and Lead Observatory}}（HALO）：這是一種[[鉛|鉛]]基中微子探測器，專門用來探測[[銀河系|銀河系]]內的[[超新星|超新星]]所產生的中微子。<ref>{{cite web|title=Home Page|url=http://www.snolab.ca/halo/|publisher=Helium and Lead Observatory}}</ref>
*電荷耦合器件暗物質探測器（Dark Matter in CCDs，DAMIC）：使用6個含有1g質量[[矽|矽]]元素的當今（2015年）最先進的[[電荷耦合器件|電荷耦合器件]]，其具有探測質量小於6GeV的[[大質量弱相互作用粒子|大質量弱相互作用粒子]]類型[[暗物質|暗物質]]的功能。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.snolab.ca/news/2012-12-10-damic-now-running-snolab|title=DAMIC now running at SNOLAB|date=2012-12-10|accessdate=2013-05-13}}</ref><ref name="Chavarria">{{Cite journal|title=DAMIC at SNOLAB|url=https://iopscience.iop.org/article/10.1088/1742-6596/1342/1/012057|last=Chavarria|first=A. E.|date=2020-01-01|journal=Journal of Physics: Conference Series|issue=1|doi=10.1088/1742-6596/1342/1/012057|volume=1342|pages=012057|issn=1742-6588|arxiv=1407.0347}}</ref>
*COUPP60氣泡室：使用裝有37kg[[過熱|過熱]]CF<sub>3</sub>I的[[氣泡室|氣泡室]]來探測[[大質量弱相互作用粒子|大質量弱相互作用粒子]]類型的暗物質。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.snolab.ca/news/2013-05-03-coupp-60-and-running-snolab|title=COUPP-60 Up and Running at SNOLAB|date=2013-05-03|accessdate=2013-05-13}}</ref>
*PICO 2L氣泡室：使用裝有2.9kg[[過熱|過熱]]C<sub>3</sub>F<sub>8</sub>的氣泡室（2公升容量）來探測[[大質量弱相互作用粒子|大質量弱相互作用粒子]]類型的暗物質。<ref name="andes2014" />{{Rp|41}}<ref>{{cite web|title=PICO-2L now running at SNOLAB!|url=https://www.snolab.ca/news/2013-11-04-pico-2l-now-running-snolab|date=2013-11-04}}</ref>
*PICO-60氣泡室：使用裝有60kg過熱C<sub>3</sub>F<sub>8</sub>的氣泡室來探測大質量弱相互作用粒子類型的暗物質。<ref>{{Cite web|title=PICO experiment: PICO 60|url=http://www.picoexperiment.com/pico60.php|accessdate=2015-08-17}}</ref>
*{{le|氬元素暗物質探測器|DEAP}}-3600（DEAP-3600）：使用3600 kg [[氬|氬]]液體來探測暗物質，靈敏度超過其它當今（2015年）最先進實驗20倍。<ref>{{Cite news|title=Biggest dark matter detector lies in wait for antisocial WIMPs|url=http://www.newscientist.com/article/mg22630184.300-biggest-dark-matter-detector-lies-in-wait-for-antisocial-wimps.html|first=Louisa|last=Field|date=23 April 2015|journal=New Scientist|issue=3108|quote=At the end of April, it will join other underground detectors worldwide in the race to find dark matter.}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://indico.cern.ch/contributionDisplay.py?contribId=54&sessionId=11&confId=214998|contribution=The DEAP-3600 Dark Matter Experiment|page=3|title=IOP 2013: High Energy and Astrop Particle Physics|publisher=Institute of Physics|first=Joseph|last=Walding|date=2013-04-10|accessdate=2013-05-19}}</ref><ref name="andes2014" />{{Rp|14,21}}

現在（2015年），還有四個實驗項目正在興建中： <ref name="current_ex" />
*{{le|SNO+|SNO+}}[[中微子|中微子]]探測器：在原本的薩探測器內，將原本使用的重水更換為液體[[閃爍體探測器|閃爍劑]]，其光輸出量更高，因此可以探測到低能量[[太陽中微子|太陽中微子]]、{{le|地球中微子|geoneutrino}}、反應爐中微子（reactor neutrino）等等。<ref>{{cite web|title=SNO+|url=http://www.snolab.ca/science/experiments/snoplus|publisher=SNOLAB}}</ref>
*{{le|迷你惰氣基低溫低能量天文物理學|Cryogenic Low-Energy Astrophysics with Neon}}（MiniCLEAN）暗物質探測器：使用[[氬|氬]]液體或[[氖|氖]]液體來探測大質量弱相互作用粒子類型的暗物質。<ref name="andes2014" />{{Rp|24–32}}<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Update on the MiniCLEAN Dark Matter Experiment|url=https://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/S1875389214006373|last=Rielage|first=K.|last2=Akashi-Ronquest|first2=M.|date=2015|journal=Physics Procedia|doi=10.1016/j.phpro.2014.12.024|volume=61|pages=144–152|language=en|arxiv=1403.4842|last3=Bodmer|first3=M.|last4=Bourque|first4=R.|last5=Buck|first5=B.|last6=Butcher|first6=A.|last7=Caldwell|first7=T.|last8=Chen|first8=Y.|last9=Coakley|first9=K.}}</ref>
* [[低溫暗物質搜尋計畫|超級低溫暗物質搜尋計畫]]（Super Cryogenic Dark Matter Search，SuperCDMS）：使用當今（2015年）最先進的低溫[[鍺|鍺]]基探測器來搜尋大質量弱相互作用粒子類型的暗物質。<ref>{{cite press release|url=http://www.snolab.ca/news/2014-07-18-second-generation-dark-matter-experiment-coming-snolab|title=Second generation dark matter experiment coming to SNOLAB|date=2014-07-18|accessdate=2014-09-18|publisher=SNOLAB}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=SLAC Summer Institute 2012|url=http://www-conf.slac.stanford.edu/ssi/2012/Presentations/Saab.pdf|contribution=The SuperCDMS Dark Matter Search|first=Tarek|last=Saab|date=2012-08-01|publisher=SLAC National Accelerator Laboratory|accessdate=2012-11-28}}</ref>
*DAMIC100探測器：使用18塊厚度為675 μm的16Mpix[[電荷耦合器件|電荷耦合器件]]來探測暗物質，合計共用到100g[[矽|矽]]元素，放射性背景事件率預期超小於1dru（#event/kg·day·keV<sub>ee</sub>）。<ref name="Chavarria" />

另有五個實驗項目已按計畫圓滿達成目標，現已關閉運作： 
*原本的重水基[[薩德伯里中微子觀測站|薩德伯里中微子觀測站]]實驗。
*[[北極星|北極星]]：這是個位於薩實驗室的地下實驗計畫，專門觀測在地球深層非常堅硬的{{le|硬岩|Underground mining (hard rock)}}所產生的[[地震學|地震信號]]。
*第一代COUPP4氣泡室：使用裝有4kg[[過熱|過熱]]CF<sub>3</sub>I的[[氣泡室|氣泡室]]來探測[[大質量弱相互作用粒子|大質量弱相互作用粒子]]類型的暗物質。<ref>{{Cite journal|title=First dark matter search results from a 4-kg CF 3 I bubble chamber operated in a deep underground site|url=https://link.aps.org/doi/10.1103/PhysRevD.86.052001|last=Behnke|first=E.|last2=Behnke|first2=J.|date=2012-09-05|journal=Physical Review D|issue=5|doi=10.1103/PhysRevD.86.052001|volume=86|pages=052001|language=en|issn=1550-7998|arxiv=1204.3094|bibcode=2012PhRvD..86e2001B|id=FERMILAB-PUB-12-098-AD-AE-CD-E-PPD|last3=Brice|first3=S. J.|last4=Broemmelsiek|first4=D.|last5=Collar|first5=J. I.|last6=Conner|first6=A.|last7=Cooper|first7=P. S.|last8=Crisler|first8=M.|last9=Dahl|first9=C. E.}}</ref>
*{{le|氬元素暗物質探測器|DEAP}}-1：使用7 kg [[氬|氬]]液體為與大質量弱相互作用粒子相互作用的標靶，主要目的是在鑑別氬液體的脈衝形狀。<ref>{{cite web|title=Dark matter Experiment with Argon and Pulse-shape discrimination|url=http://www.snolab.ca/deap1/index.html|publisher=DEAP-1}}</ref>
*{{le|加拿大探索超對稱物體計畫|PICASSO (dark matter)}}：使用過熱的C<sub>4</sub>F<sub>10</sub>液體，以小液滴形式分散在[[聚合物|聚合]]介質或[[黏性|黏性]]介質內，可以用來探測暗物質。假設有暗物質與小液滴發生碰撞，則小液滴會變換為氣泡，並且伴隨著可記錄的聲脈衝。<ref>{{Cite conference|first=Nigel|last=Smith|title=Advanced Instrumentation Techniques in SNOLAB|date=17 June 2015|url=https://indico.cern.ch/event/355942/session/231/contribution/793/attachments/707040/970666/2015_CAP_SNOLAB_Instrumentation.pdf|conference=2015 Canadian Association of Physicists Congress|conference-url=http://www.cap.ca/en/congress/2015}}</ref>{{Rp|3}}

薩實驗室正在考慮添加更多實驗計畫，例如，下一代{{le|冨集氙觀測站|Enriched Xenon Observatory}}（nEXO）<ref>{{Cite conference|title=The SNOLAB Science Programme|date=12 September 2013|last=Sinclair|first=David|url=https://conferences.lbl.gov/event/36/session/35/contribution/216/material/slides/0.pdf|conference=13th International Conference on Topics in Astroparticle and Underground Physics|7=|location=Asilomar, California|accessdate=2014-11-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161224033759/https://conferences.lbl.gov/event/36/session/35/contribution/216/material/slides/0.pdf|archive-date=2016-12-24|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{Cite conference|title=Searching for neutrino-less double beta decay with EXO-200 and nEXO|url=http://www.ba.infn.it/~now/now2014/web-content/TALKS/aMon/Par1/NOW_POCAR.pdf|first=Andrea|last=Pocar|date=8 September 2014|conference=Neutrino Oscillation Workshop|conference-url=http://www.ba.infn.it/~now/now2014/|location=Otranto|accessdate=2015-01-10}}</ref>{{Rp|16}}、探索[[雙β衰變#無中微子雙β衰變|無中微子雙貝他衰變]]的{{le|眼鏡蛇實驗|COBRA experiment}}<ref name="Asilomar2013">{{Citation|contribution-url=https://commons.lbl.gov/download/attachments/95551642/NigelSmith_CJPL%20Workshop_SNOLAB.pdf|contribution=Infrastructure Development for underground labs—SNOLAB experience|first=Nigel J.T.|last=Smith|title=13th International Conference on Topics in Astroparticle and Underground Physics|location=Asilomar, California|date=2013-09-08}}</ref>{{Rp|27}}、發展圓球形氣體探測器來探測暗物質的{{le|新圓球實驗|New Experiments With Spheres}}（NEWS）<ref>{{Cite web|title=NEWS: New Experiments With Spheres|url=https://www.snolab.ca/news-projects/|accessdate=2015-08-16}}</ref>。薩實驗室計畫興建一個更大的PICO-250L氣泡室 <ref name="andes2014" />{{Rp|44}}。

